content:
SetValueOverride Delegate

Definition

Allows a custom override of the stem.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue* logic associated with a dependency property that is defined on a dependency object.

In this Article

public delegate void SetValueOverride(DependencyObject d, object value);
Inheritance
Object
Delegate
SetValueOverride

Remarks

Note

This material discusses types and namespaces that are obsolete. For more information, see Deprecated Types in Windows Workflow Foundation 4.5.

The implementation of this delegate can be set to the SetValueOverride property of PropertyMetadata while calling Register or RegisterAttached.
